The core idea for Double DQN is to decouple the action
evaluation and action selection. Double DQN uses target
network to select the action and use another local network
to evaluate the Q-value. In such a way, we can avoid over-
estimation problems of action [3], [8]. And it would help the
network to better learn unbiased values. The algorithm for
